{"tid":1412154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼續罷工 光復香港 時代革命","createTime":"2019-08-05T05:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T06:05:26.000Z","uid":244242,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ae946069bffac8edd412f3da7b1c35594639baa0","tid":1412154,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:37:41.000Z","msg":"繼續罷工 唔好比佢停落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n恆指日日跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登日日興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每日插水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  每日跌港幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n航班全線暫停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政府同市民共同攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時就抗爭成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一眾連登仔準備攞BNO飛去英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留低我地哩啲窮L繼續乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港真係多得連登唔少<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加油啊 連登仔 香港好快變死港<br />\n光！復！香！港！<br />\n時！代！革！命！<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"5a8c159af00bad931022e2380ac4a3e8b5142379","tid":1412154,"uid":244242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:39:12.000Z","msg":"工 繼續丟~~"},{"pid":"47c92a16e2f5470ab12ba7376183525d3d09e8f3","tid":1412154,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:39:53.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"dd36da1bc06fb983197e16aca2841fc13a1e8a87","tid":1412154,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:40:05.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"f939cd93c90818f4353981f9eedb3593cdcab02a","tid":1412154,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"63e0bf05156